headline.main: HIDDEN TANK ARMY PROTECTS MOSCOW; Innumerable Machines Ready to Dart From Underground Garages, Germans Say

lead_paragraph: BERLIN, Nov. 11 (AP) -- Underground garages from, which Russian tanks and armored cars can speed to the attack form a part of the intricate fortification system protecting Moscow, German dispatches from the front said tonight.
